msgid "Before you publish"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:7
msgid "Ensure:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:9
msgid ""
"The service identifier is filled in (it is used to construct the dataset URL)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:10
msgid "The **Validate** button shows no errors"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:11
msgid "You have a TriplyDB API token with write access to the target dataset"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:20
msgid "Publishing"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:22
msgid ""
"Click the **Publish** button in the bottom-right of the application (purple)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:23
msgid "Enter your TriplyDB credentials:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:23
msgid ""
"**Base URL:** `https://api.open-regels.triply.cc` (or your own instance)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:23
msgid "**Account:** your TriplyDB account or organisation name"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:23
msgid "**Dataset:** the target dataset name"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:23
msgid "**API Token:** create one in TriplyDB → User Settings → API Tokens"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:28
msgid ""
"Optionally click **Test Connection** to verify the credentials without "
"uploading."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:29
msgid "Click **Publish to TriplyDB**."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:38
msgid "Progress tracking"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:40
msgid "The dialog shows four steps with real-time status:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:42
msgid "Validating form"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:43
msgid "Generating TTL"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:44
msgid "Uploading to TriplyDB"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:45
msgid "Updating service via backend proxy"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:47
msgid ""
"On success, a direct link to the published dataset appears and the dialog "
"closes automatically after two seconds. A green message with the dataset URL "
"appears under the page title and auto-dismisses after ten seconds."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:51
msgid "Error handling"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:53
msgid ""
"Errors are displayed inside the dialog with details. The dialog closes after "
"five seconds and an inline red message appears under the page title. Common "
"causes include invalid credentials, a non-existent account or dataset name, "
"or network issues."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:57
msgid "API token security"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:59
msgid ""
"Your API token is stored in browser localStorage on your device only. It is "
"transmitted exclusively to the configured TriplyDB API endpoint over HTTPS. "
"It is never sent to any other server."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:61
msgid "Best practices:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:62
msgid ""
"Create tokens with the minimum permissions needed (write access to the "
"specific dataset)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:63
msgid "Rotate tokens regularly via TriplyDB → User Settings → API Tokens"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:64
msgid "Never share tokens or commit them to version control"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:68
msgid "Cumulative publishing"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cpublishing-to-triplydb.md:70
msgid ""
"Each time you publish, the service data is added to the dataset. The backend "
"proxy provides a unified SPARQL endpoint that queries across all uploads, so "
"the dataset always reflects the complete current state of all published "
"services. Publishing the same service again after edits results in the "
"updated version being available alongside the previous one in TriplyDB, with "
"the unified endpoint showing the most recent data."
msgstr ""
